high_descs: Turn around and go to the desk in the bedroom.
Take the knife from the table.
Turn around and go to the living room.
Cut the tomato into pieces using the knife.
Then put the knife on the diningtable.
Take the tomato from the table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the tomato into the sink and washed it.
Then take it out and go near the microwave.
Put the tomato into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Placed the tomato into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and head down the passage and reach the bedroom on the left to reach the desk.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn right to exit the room and turn right to head down the passage and turn right to reach the tomato on the white table.
Cut the tomato on the table with the knife.
Put the knife on the diningtable.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Turn left and head down the passage to reach the sink.
Wash the tomato in the sink and take it out.
Turn around to walk down the passage and reach the kitchen on the left to face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed tomato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk down the hall, go into a bedroom on the far left, and stand facing the desk.
Pick up the knife that is on the desk.
Take the knife with the tomato to the living room, and stand facing both the coffee table and the loveseat.
Slice the tomato that is on the coffee table once with the knife.
Put the knife down on the diningtable behind the tomato.
Pick up the smaller sliced part of the tomato.
Carry the tomato slice to the sink in the bathroom at the other end of the hall.
Rinse the tomato slice in the bathroom sink.
Carry the tomato slice to the kitchen, and stand directly in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave door, put the tomato slice in the microwave, and close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Prepare and microwave a Tomato slice.
